# Project Importance

Many small companies and non-tech organizations cannot afford enterprise-grade security solutions like Cloudflare or Akamai.

This project aims to provide:

* Affordable security
* Self-hosted deployment
* Easy integration into existing Flask apps
* Real-time attack prevention
* AI-assisted threat detection

Suitable for:

* E-commerce websites
* Admin dashboards
* Institutional portals
* Startup web applications
* Internal enterprise tools

